# claude2026-emotions-finegrained.twlist
#
# Sub-vocabularies for major emotional categories. Lets a grammar pick
# specifically "a fear word" or "a joy adjective" instead of any general
# mood word. Words are tagged by the emotion they evoke; many overlap
# parts of speech (noun/adjective/verb forms grouped together intentionally).

